{
  "stem": "24231.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a lot of Christian I had a lot of friends, whom I am still in contact today, who are still living, who were my friends.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Most of them from that era are Christians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In, in the area where I was, the Czech weren't anti-Semitic in that-- in that area.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't say I ever felt, being-- you know, being discriminated in any way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happened is when Hitler came to power and there was an upheaval in Europe, a lot of Polish Jews came to, to Prague.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of German Jews came to Prague.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they started to speak German and started to speak also Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to the Czechs, Germans were something which was-- which was always against the Czechs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they associated the Jews with the Germans, and that's when you started to see little anti-Semitic talks, because of the language.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also, some of them were Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have to say that lot of-- before this upheaval, a lot of Jews in, in Czechoslovakia didn't-- weren't really true orthodox, wearing the black, black hats and coats.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there was not much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And on top of that, they were mostly in the center of Prague, downtown, so there was not much anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The anti-Semitism really came through Eastern Czechoslovakia where also there was a trial at one time after the, the war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A Jewish fellow was accused of during Passover that he killed somebody and used the blood for--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no this is after the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the war.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was after.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is-- and at that time, the President of Czechoslovakia, Masaryk, stepped in, and he defended because there is no such thing, that, you know, Jews take blood.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
